projects.description: Leading a multidisciplinary team of seven, we created a web media library to host and manage media assets for cinemas. As part of a proof of concept project, we built the Media Library with an Angular front end, C# dotNet back end implementing a REST API, and leveraged Cloudflare technologies to compare the current industry standard Cloud Service Providers; AWS Cloud and Azure Cloud.
